s that are\r\nvisiting the country and need to travel from one point to another.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:35.4pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">With that it has a fleet of vehicles that need\r\nto be documented, managed well and records of the vehicles; the routes they are\r\ntravelling to, the number of tourists each vehicle has, the drivers assigned to\r\neach vehicle need to be recorded and documented properly for easy management\r\nand future reference.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:35.4pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">The existing system that the company uses is\r\ncompletely manual. The system is based on paper works and communications\r\nbetween the people handling the vehicles i.e. managers, drivers, and the\r\nclients (tourists).</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:35.4pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Once the company gets requests from the tourists,\r\nthe manager has to check manually if there is any vehicle that is available,\r\nthen assign it to driver who will intern have to call the clients and set up\r\nthe meeting place.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:35.4pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">This Kind of managing system has all kinds of\r\nfails and problems. By identifying these weaknesses such as not being able to\r\nfully keep track of the vehicles, an online management system is what the\r\nclient (Silver Africa Tours and Safaris), needs. It does the management of the vehicles,\r\ndriver information, keep track of the progress and also keep records of the\r\nclients that use the vehicles.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:35.4pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">The system is a web based and an android\r\napplication that can be accessed by both the client to Silver Africa, drivers\r\nand Silver Africa management, hence it will do away with the manual system that\r\nis currently in use.</span></p>\r\n\r\n										\r\n										', 'aboutus'),
